headline: Live Nation Is the Company Consumers Love to Hate. But Investors Love It.
summary: Good luck finding many sports or music enthusiasts who like  Live Nation Entertainment  —the concert promoter and venue owner that is also the parent company of Ticketmaster.  In short, Live Nation is an easy target for criticism.  Investors love Live Nation about as much as fans of Taylor Swift and Oasis loathe it.
